<section id="body">
	<media class="leftFloat" src="../Media/DD_LN1a.mp3" mode="4" id="1002"  /><img class="rightFloat" src="../Media/DD_LN_002.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"  /><p align="left"><b>1 Which areas of the world does Voluntary Workers International send people to work in?</b><g id="1">A  South America</g><g id="2">B  Central America</g><g id="3">C  Africa</g><g id="4">D  Asia</g><g id="5">E  Eastern Europe</g></p><p align="left"><b>2 What does James Lewis say that volunteers bring to local communities?</b><g id="6">A  their ideas</g><g id="7">B  their professionalism</g><g id="8">C  their skills</g><g id="9">D  their wisdom</g><g id="10">E  their experience</g></p><p align="left"><b>3 What does he say that volunteers gain from their experiences?</b><g id="11">A  new friends</g><g id="12">B  knowledge of different cultures</g><g id="13">C  knowledge about themselves</g><g id="14">D  increased expertise</g><g id="15">E  a career</g></p>
</section>
<section id="fb1">
	<p align="left">1A. James does not mention South America in any context.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb2">
	<p align="left">1B. James does not mention Central America in any context.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb3">
	<p align="left">1C. James says the volunteers are sent to developing countries in Africa.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb4">
	<p align="left">1D. James says that volunteers are sent to developing countries in Africa.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb5">
	<p align="left">1E. James says they hope to move into Eastern Europe shortly not that they are already sending volunteers there.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb6">
	<p align="left">2A. James doesn't mention 'ideas'.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb7">
	<p align="left">2B. James doesn't mention 'professionalism'.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb8">
	<p align="left">2C. James says the volunteers share their skills with the local people. People make up communities.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb9">
	<p align="left">2D. James does not mention wisdom.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb10">
	<p align="left">2E. James says they share their experience with local people. People make up communities.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb11">
	<p align="left">3A. James says that volunteers talk about the friendships they've made.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb12">
	<p align="left">3B. James doesn't mention this.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb13">
	<p align="left">3C. James doesn't mention this.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb14">
	<p align="left">3D. James says volunteers talk about the new skills they've learnt. Expertise has a similar meaning to skill.</p>
</section>
